snippet.title: Catamancer Pre-alpha Gameplay
snippet.description:
Catamancer Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/dysprosium/catamancer-0

This video shows a game between Dys and Sil, the lead developers of Catamancer. Keep in mind that this is pre-alpha footage, so there are bugs and glitches and much of the art, sound and animations is unfinished. Enjoy!

- And yes, we are aware we made 2 editing mistakes. Derp derp!
- Dammit! And I call the Leopard a Jaguar at some point. I need more sleep! ;)

Music used: Setting Sail, The Hyperborean Menace, The Land of the Wizard, Battle of Kings, Queen of the Night, Escape from the Temple & Beyond the Stars by Per Kiilstofte https://machinimasound.com/music/mood/epic/
Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
